Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏會後  轉學到音大附屬的君原春美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉學後不久就拿下了全國大賽的優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.78,0:24:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.73,0:24:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了獎學金  聽說還可以去留學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這塊手帕  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.12,0:24:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.37,0:24:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是朋友給我的禮物
